WEBVTT

01:27.968 --> 01:35.104
=The Legend of ShenLi=

01:35.728 --> 01:39.152
=Episode 1=

01:42.192 --> 01:45.104
(Lunar New Year's Eve)

01:46.147 --> 01:47.827
The fireworks are so pretty.

02:01.680 --> 02:03.344
So pretty!

02:05.904 --> 02:08.107
It's my turn!

02:13.360 --> 02:14.384
A dud.

02:15.786 --> 02:17.107
She set off a dud.

02:17.107 --> 02:18.786
- A dud.
- A dud.

02:19.627 --> 02:21.467
She set off a dud.

02:21.987 --> 02:22.992
A dud.

02:23.987 --> 02:27.586
- A dud.
- A dud.

02:27.586 --> 02:28.946
A dud.

02:29.616 --> 02:30.640
Let's go.

02:31.152 --> 02:32.666
Let's light the lanterns.

02:33.306 --> 02:34.866
Those lanterns look amazing.

03:08.227 --> 03:09.268
By decree of Her Holiness,

03:09.268 --> 03:10.908
come with us now, Lord Bicang.

03:12.080 --> 03:13.392
I won't go back.

03:13.392 --> 03:14.427
No one can make me.

03:17.104 --> 03:18.147
Her Holiness has agreed

03:18.147 --> 03:19.248
to your political marriage

03:19.248 --> 03:20.304
with the Divine Realm.

03:20.304 --> 03:21.468
Please don't act willfully.

03:23.028 --> 03:24.427
I'm Lord Bicang of the Immortal Realm.

03:25.067 --> 03:26.707
I will not marry that fickle loser.

03:27.600 --> 03:28.720
General Zhufei.

03:28.720 --> 03:30.347
There's no way I'm marrying him.

03:32.028 --> 03:33.668
Forgive us, Your Lordship.

03:37.308 --> 03:38.388
You dare to stop me?

03:38.896 --> 03:39.908
Impressive.

03:40.816 --> 03:41.936
Very well.

03:41.936 --> 03:43.147
Bring it on.

03:47.427 --> 03:48.627
Mofang, stay calm.

05:18.148 --> 05:19.868
Please come with us, Your Lordship.

05:19.868 --> 05:21.428
Don't give us a hard time.

05:21.428 --> 05:22.448
Are you done?

05:22.448 --> 05:23.504
Step aside!

05:24.507 --> 05:25.747
You're killing me.

06:05.828 --> 06:07.408
This firework is so pretty.

06:07.408 --> 06:09.347
So pretty!

06:20.336 --> 06:21.388
What are you doing?

06:21.388 --> 06:22.448
Trying to scare me?

06:25.828 --> 06:27.152
Mofang, don't be impulsive.

06:27.152 --> 06:28.627
Don't hurt Her Lordship.

06:49.072 --> 06:50.128
My Lord.

06:53.988 --> 06:55.280
That's all I can do for you.

06:56.400 --> 06:57.488
Take care.

07:10.896 --> 07:11.920
(Good for you.)

07:12.708 --> 07:13.712
(Very loyal.)

07:14.268 --> 07:15.507
(That's my subordinate.)

07:19.792 --> 07:20.944
Your Lordship!

07:42.384 --> 07:43.388
Mofang!

07:43.388 --> 07:44.668
How can you hurt Her Lordship?

08:05.948 --> 08:06.960
Something is wrong.

08:32.330 --> 08:33.788
(Qingsheng City, Mortal Realm)

08:33.788 --> 08:34.800
Here you are.

08:35.312 --> 08:36.400
See you around.

08:43.307 --> 08:44.400
Here you go.

08:45.867 --> 08:47.600
Her Lordship seems to have fallen here.

08:47.600 --> 08:48.624
Listen.

08:48.624 --> 08:50.067
You search to the east. I'll go west.

08:50.667 --> 08:52.468
Let's meet here in an hour.

09:02.448 --> 09:04.388
- I've packed it for you.
- Here you are.

09:04.388 --> 09:05.392
Please try it.

09:06.992 --> 09:08.016
See you around.

09:21.348 --> 09:22.348
Would you like a chicken?

09:22.348 --> 09:23.536
Which one?

09:23.536 --> 09:25.328
This one is quite special.

09:26.067 --> 09:27.148
It's a bit ugly.

09:27.148 --> 09:28.507
I caught it on the mountain yesterday.

09:29.148 --> 09:30.348
The tail feathers are burnt.

09:31.187 --> 09:32.307
Get a better one.

09:32.944 --> 09:34.064
No need.

09:34.064 --> 09:35.088
I want this one.

09:35.747 --> 09:37.307
Okay, I'll give you a discount.

09:38.160 --> 09:39.216
No need.

09:39.824 --> 09:41.808
It's worth the price.

09:42.427 --> 09:43.504
It would be upset

09:44.028 --> 09:45.360
if it's sold at a bargain.

09:45.360 --> 09:46.708
It's just a chicken.

10:29.747 --> 10:30.828
You butcher.

10:32.067 --> 10:33.187
Let go of me.

10:34.588 --> 10:35.664
Let go.

10:36.187 --> 10:37.456
Stop pulling.

10:37.968 --> 10:39.024
Stop.

10:42.148 --> 10:43.344
You woke up?

10:43.344 --> 10:45.264
I thought you were going to die.

10:45.264 --> 10:46.547
Cluck Cluck.

10:46.547 --> 10:48.080
- Come and eat.
- (Why do I sound like this?)

10:52.784 --> 10:53.872
How dare you!

10:54.427 --> 10:57.148
I am the formidable lord
of the Immortal Realm,

10:57.148 --> 10:58.896
who pacifies wars
with my silver spear in hand.

10:58.896 --> 10:59.920
No one dares

10:59.920 --> 11:00.987
to disrespect me.

11:01.744 --> 11:02.800
How dare you, a mortal,

11:03.312 --> 11:05.067
treat me like a fowl?

11:05.588 --> 11:06.736
This is unacceptable!

11:13.388 --> 11:14.480
No hurry.

11:14.480 --> 11:16.067
There's still plenty here.

11:19.468 --> 11:20.496
Where is my spiritual power?

11:25.296 --> 11:26.388
Who needs your food?

11:30.307 --> 11:31.307
Forget it then.

11:31.824 --> 11:33.744
Let's take a bath first.

11:36.788 --> 11:37.840
Who's taking a bath?

11:39.536 --> 11:40.688
Don't touch me.

11:40.688 --> 11:41.867
What are you doing?

11:41.867 --> 11:43.120
You! How dare you!

11:43.120 --> 11:44.176
Why are you poking me?

11:44.176 --> 11:45.264
How dare you!

11:45.264 --> 11:47.067
Do it again and see what happens.

11:47.067 --> 11:48.148
Time to take a bath.

11:52.560 --> 11:53.616
Help...

11:55.728 --> 11:56.816
I can't drink anymore.

11:59.468 --> 12:00.656
I really can't...

12:02.388 --> 12:03.547
Not great with water.

12:09.828 --> 12:10.867
Is it drowning?

12:28.867 --> 12:29.872
So much water...

12:30.768 --> 12:32.176
Keep breathing.

12:32.176 --> 12:33.520
Remember,

12:33.520 --> 12:34.576
you won't die as long as

12:35.307 --> 12:36.368
you keep breathing.

12:36.987 --> 12:38.107
Easier said than done.

12:39.312 --> 12:40.427
This evil man

12:40.427 --> 12:41.667
is torturing me on purpose.

12:42.708 --> 12:43.788
I'll get even with you

12:44.468 --> 12:45.627
once I recover.

12:46.948 --> 12:48.708
One must be polite.

12:53.028 --> 12:54.128
My name is Xingyun.

12:55.067 --> 12:56.507
I don't go by "evil man".

12:58.588 --> 12:59.627
Poor swimmer.

13:35.747 --> 13:37.107
(Now that I look at him,)

13:37.747 --> 13:40.148
(there are hints
of indifference and holiness.)

13:49.788 --> 13:50.832
Time for medicine.

13:58.064 --> 13:59.152
My feet got numb.

14:07.088 --> 14:08.148
(I was mistaken.)

14:08.867 --> 14:10.148
(He is totally ordinary.)

14:21.268 --> 14:23.388
(The little torment actually)

14:23.987 --> 14:25.348
(helped me regain strength.)

14:27.152 --> 14:28.208
(Not bad.)

14:37.648 --> 14:38.672
(No.)

14:38.672 --> 14:40.268
(Still no spiritual power.)

14:41.708 --> 14:42.908
(I knew I couldn't)

14:42.908 --> 14:43.948
(get it back so fast.)

14:44.848 --> 14:45.936
(But it may be good.)

14:46.547 --> 14:48.828
(The Immortal Realm
can't detect my presence.)

14:49.348 --> 14:50.948
(But it's only a matter of time)

14:51.547 --> 14:52.948
(before Her Holiness finds me.)

14:53.468 --> 14:54.512
(If I haven't regained)

14:54.512 --> 14:56.067
(my spiritual power by then...)

14:56.784 --> 14:57.808
Cluck Cluck.

15:01.904 --> 15:02.992
Food is ready.

15:04.348 --> 15:05.424
(As if I care.)

15:12.336 --> 15:13.360
Come on.

15:13.872 --> 15:14.928
(This is awkward.)

15:22.544 --> 15:23.632
Put it here.

15:28.912 --> 15:30.000
Hurry up.

15:33.828 --> 15:35.667
(Why is there
a faint scent of medicine?)

15:36.867 --> 15:38.388
(Lips turning black.)

15:38.388 --> 15:39.427
(Slight dark circles.)

15:40.588 --> 15:41.712
(Signs of a short lifespan.)

15:42.672 --> 15:44.348
(So he's a sickly fella.)

15:45.667 --> 15:46.828
(Well, well.)

15:46.828 --> 15:48.880
(This mortal
has seen me as an underdog.)

15:49.398 --> 15:50.468
(But he won't live long.)

15:51.028 --> 15:52.656
(He will die and forget everything.)

15:52.656 --> 15:53.828
(And I)

15:53.828 --> 15:55.788
(will still be
the impeccable Lord Bicang.)

15:57.948 --> 15:59.344
(I am still flawless.)

16:00.080 --> 16:01.104
(Very good.)

16:02.224 --> 16:03.268
The feather...

16:03.268 --> 16:04.368
How dare you!

16:09.708 --> 16:10.788
(It smells quite nice.)

16:13.296 --> 16:14.352
(Let me try it.)

16:16.080 --> 16:17.936
(This...)

16:17.936 --> 16:19.344
(This pastry)

16:19.344 --> 16:20.688
(is way too tasty.)

16:23.120 --> 16:24.240
(So tasty.)

16:30.547 --> 16:31.708
(It's too good to be true.)

16:38.788 --> 16:39.888
(Not bad.)

16:40.912 --> 16:42.000
How dare you!

16:42.000 --> 16:43.312
You're looking down at me.

16:43.984 --> 16:45.872
Everyone admires and respects me

16:45.872 --> 16:47.148
in the Immortal Realm.

16:47.148 --> 16:48.348
Men shiver when they

16:48.348 --> 16:49.360
see me passing by.

16:49.867 --> 16:51.536
Yet he dares to look down at me.

16:53.008 --> 16:54.187
Never mind.

16:54.187 --> 16:56.144
Considering that he's a fine chef,

16:57.507 --> 16:58.544
I'll let him off.

17:02.480 --> 17:03.600
That's it?

17:06.032 --> 17:08.080
Get me more.

17:09.552 --> 17:10.832
Hurry up.

17:10.832 --> 17:11.952
Get going.

17:12.667 --> 17:13.936
That's all

17:13.936 --> 17:15.280
I made today.

17:15.280 --> 17:16.748
I'll make some more another day.

17:17.488 --> 17:18.800
How dare you!

17:18.800 --> 17:19.868
You think you can

17:19.868 --> 17:21.008
brush me off like that?

17:21.628 --> 17:22.948
You should have made some more.

17:23.504 --> 17:24.592
I should head out now.

17:25.264 --> 17:26.352
Cluck Cluck.

17:27.307 --> 17:28.464
Guard the place.

17:29.267 --> 17:30.320
I have a lot to sell, myself.

17:31.408 --> 17:32.432
(Sell himself?)

17:33.552 --> 17:34.628
(In broad daylight,)

17:34.628 --> 17:35.628
(a fine young man like him)

17:36.307 --> 17:37.348
(chooses to)

17:38.147 --> 17:39.708
(make a living by selling himself?)

17:43.088 --> 17:44.336
(What a shame.)

17:44.336 --> 17:45.424
(It's dangerous here.)

17:46.128 --> 17:47.152
(I must leave.)

17:48.336 --> 17:49.424
(Bad luck.)

17:52.787 --> 17:53.787
(I can't even fly away)

17:53.787 --> 17:55.187
(without spiritual power.)

17:57.936 --> 17:58.960
(Burglar!)

18:05.588 --> 18:07.147
(A clumsy burglar.)

18:08.432 --> 18:09.547
(She's only)

18:09.547 --> 18:10.547
(hurting herself.)

18:15.228 --> 18:16.948
(Let me see
what you're trying to steal.)

18:22.640 --> 18:23.787
(So she's not a burglar)

18:24.547 --> 18:25.787
(but the River Snail Maiden.)

18:27.344 --> 18:28.464
(For that guy?)

18:31.187 --> 18:32.267
(So diligent.)

18:33.828 --> 18:34.896
(She's a good girl.)

18:40.048 --> 18:41.187
(Still here?)

18:41.187 --> 18:42.427
What should I do?

18:44.147 --> 18:46.027
How am I going to live if I can't

18:46.027 --> 18:47.472
see Xingyun again?

18:47.472 --> 18:49.988
(So she's into that sickly fella.)

18:50.508 --> 18:52.147
(I'll let her be.)

18:55.988 --> 18:57.427
Why is Xingyun

18:58.147 --> 19:00.208
keeping such a fat chicken?

19:00.208 --> 19:01.228
(Is she talking about me?)

19:01.228 --> 19:02.828
I might as well cook it for him.

19:02.828 --> 19:03.948
(Does she hear herself?)

19:05.307 --> 19:06.576
Stay away from me!

19:06.576 --> 19:07.667
(Oh no.)

19:07.667 --> 19:08.912
(I have no spiritual power.)

19:08.912 --> 19:10.147
(I'm doomed)

19:10.147 --> 19:11.280
(if I get stewed.)

19:16.400 --> 19:17.488
(That was close.)

19:18.868 --> 19:19.948
S-Stay back.

19:19.948 --> 19:21.136
Stay back.

19:24.427 --> 19:25.456
Stop running.

19:25.968 --> 19:26.988
I give up, okay?

19:26.988 --> 19:28.432
I'm not stupid.

19:28.432 --> 19:29.468
Anyone would run.

19:29.468 --> 19:30.864
- Listen.
- Stay back.

19:30.864 --> 19:32.688
- Let's talk.
- That's about enough.

19:32.688 --> 19:33.808
Don't run.

19:34.352 --> 19:35.376
Tell me.

19:35.920 --> 19:36.944
How do I

19:36.944 --> 19:38.192
catch a chicken?

19:46.608 --> 19:47.632
(Oh no.)

19:51.387 --> 19:53.027
(Today, I finally got a taste)

19:53.968 --> 19:55.184
(of the sorrow)

19:55.184 --> 19:56.667
(of a powerless victim.)

20:03.547 --> 20:05.108
(I, Lord ShenLi, hereby make an oath.)

20:05.108 --> 20:06.267
Behave.

20:06.267 --> 20:07.427
(A blood oath.)

20:07.427 --> 20:09.168
(If I get stewed today,)

20:09.168 --> 20:10.448
(I shall fight my way)

20:11.024 --> 20:12.508
(to heaven to make it even)

20:12.508 --> 20:14.067
(with that heedless god)

20:14.667 --> 20:15.828
(who assigned my marriage!)

20:20.432 --> 20:21.488
What are you doing?

20:22.267 --> 20:23.344
Xingyun.

20:23.344 --> 20:24.708
I just came to see you.

20:25.456 --> 20:26.547
And I found

20:26.547 --> 20:28.027
this plump chicken.

20:28.027 --> 20:29.067
You know what?

20:29.067 --> 20:30.427
You must stew it today.

20:30.427 --> 20:31.427
Or it won't taste good.

20:32.508 --> 20:33.520
You can't cook it.

20:34.067 --> 20:35.152
What took you so long?

20:35.824 --> 20:36.912
Thank goodness.

20:37.468 --> 20:38.508
I almost got cooked.

20:39.228 --> 20:40.240
I'm sorry. I...

20:40.748 --> 20:42.588
I just wanted to leave you something

20:42.588 --> 20:43.988
before I go.

20:45.968 --> 20:47.027
Tomorrow,

20:47.027 --> 20:49.168
my father is taking me
down south to do business.

20:49.168 --> 20:50.352
Perhaps,

20:50.907 --> 20:52.628
I will never see you again.

20:52.628 --> 20:53.708
But I haven't really

20:53.708 --> 20:54.736
seen you much, anyway.

20:55.248 --> 20:56.307
It's not like that.

20:56.307 --> 20:57.667
I was seeing you every day,

20:59.027 --> 21:00.508
in secret.

21:00.508 --> 21:01.588
What a pity.

21:02.096 --> 21:03.440
I don't think

21:03.440 --> 21:04.588
I've ever seen you before.

21:09.267 --> 21:10.896
(Why does he say that?)

21:10.896 --> 21:11.952
Indeed.

21:13.136 --> 21:14.288
Not even once.

21:15.868 --> 21:17.108
Don't tell me that

21:17.108 --> 21:19.600
you're here for a farewell gift.

21:19.600 --> 21:20.848
(This sickly fella)

21:20.848 --> 21:22.387
(sounds so mean.)

21:22.387 --> 21:24.468
I don't have anything fancy.

21:26.307 --> 21:27.508
If you don't mind it,

21:28.187 --> 21:30.147
please accept this piece of cloth.

21:35.216 --> 21:36.272
No need.

21:37.040 --> 21:38.128
No need.

21:39.988 --> 21:41.187
It's a fine piece of cloth.

21:48.868 --> 21:50.868
Could you please close the door?

21:58.468 --> 21:59.696
The River Snail Maiden

21:59.696 --> 22:00.752
is heartbroken.

22:04.828 --> 22:06.187
What a nice girl.

22:06.187 --> 22:07.216
She's a bit silly.

22:08.147 --> 22:09.552
But she's kind-hearted.

22:09.552 --> 22:11.312
How did she fall for someone

22:11.312 --> 22:12.400
in this line of work

22:12.400 --> 22:13.708
who's also cold and mean?

22:14.468 --> 22:16.027
What line of work?

22:16.027 --> 22:17.267
You just went out to sell...

22:17.267 --> 22:18.320
That line of work.

22:19.907 --> 22:21.027
(You caught me.)

22:22.427 --> 22:23.440
Are you talking to me?

22:25.748 --> 22:27.988
Can't you tell who I'm talking to?

22:30.228 --> 22:31.984
You...

22:31.984 --> 22:33.628
You, you sickly fella...

22:35.508 --> 22:36.828
Am I hallucinating?

22:38.187 --> 22:39.787
Are you really talking to me?

22:39.787 --> 22:41.040
That's right.

22:41.040 --> 22:42.832
I am talking to you.

22:42.832 --> 22:44.720
You could hear me all along?

22:44.720 --> 22:45.776
Were you toying with me?

22:49.708 --> 22:50.907
I was toying with you.

22:53.680 --> 22:54.800
Also,

22:55.667 --> 22:56.708
my name is Xingyun.

22:57.264 --> 22:58.352
Remember that well.

22:59.184 --> 23:00.304
Besides,

23:00.304 --> 23:01.520
what's wrong with my job?

23:02.748 --> 23:03.907
What's wrong with your job

23:04.464 --> 23:05.520
or toying with me?

23:06.348 --> 23:08.228
Do you have a conscience?

23:08.868 --> 23:10.628
How can you say that so casually?

23:11.147 --> 23:12.228
Are you a monster?

23:14.267 --> 23:15.344
I'm only

23:15.868 --> 23:17.547
doing my job and toying with you.

23:21.108 --> 23:23.228
And you make it
sound like a heinous crime.

23:23.888 --> 23:24.944
Fine.

23:24.944 --> 23:26.224
I'll do it

23:26.224 --> 23:27.468
behind your back next time.

23:29.008 --> 23:30.096
This is infuriating.

23:31.067 --> 23:32.144
The stove is on.

23:35.108 --> 23:36.708
(This guy is sinister.)

23:37.667 --> 23:38.667
(I must leave now.)

23:39.628 --> 23:41.136
(Otherwise, I may end up)

23:41.136 --> 23:42.468
(tortured to death.)

24:24.988 --> 24:26.128
(I can't even fly out)

24:26.128 --> 24:27.588
(without spiritual power.)

24:27.588 --> 24:28.592
Cluck Cluck.

24:29.520 --> 24:30.640
Time to eat.

24:43.787 --> 24:45.108
(Smells amazing.)

24:48.976 --> 24:50.224
(Let me eat first.)

24:57.680 --> 24:58.704
(Done.)

24:59.280 --> 25:00.368
(I'm out of here.)

25:05.040 --> 25:06.064
Come back.

25:07.376 --> 25:08.400
What do you want?

25:15.147 --> 25:16.304
Don't touch me.

25:19.792 --> 25:20.816
Go away.

25:24.708 --> 25:26.147
Don't you love sunbathing?

25:27.147 --> 25:28.208
Why would I?

25:29.667 --> 25:30.787
The sun is there every day.

25:45.187 --> 25:47.056
(We're leaving...)

25:47.056 --> 25:48.748
(We're leaving...)

26:09.868 --> 26:11.307
It dried up fast today.

26:12.135 --> 26:13.664
(For coughing up blood)

26:20.080 --> 26:21.552
(One quarter past Wu hour,)

26:26.672 --> 26:29.328
(the 15th of the 8th month, Age 20)

26:35.014 --> 26:38.878
(Time of leaf fall)

27:43.868 --> 27:45.067
She's good-looking.

29:10.108 --> 29:11.468
Who covered me with a gown?

29:19.828 --> 29:21.008
Tao.

29:21.008 --> 29:22.064
Let's go.

29:30.448 --> 29:31.696
Xingyun.

29:31.696 --> 29:33.228
I'm here to say goodbye.

29:34.067 --> 29:35.948
I'd like to have a few words with you.

29:35.948 --> 29:37.104
I'm sure the south

29:38.228 --> 29:39.787
is covered with peach blossoms now.

29:44.336 --> 29:45.360
I am not the one.

29:47.664 --> 29:50.672
(He's so cold and distant.)

29:50.672 --> 29:52.907
I'm never coming back here

29:53.667 --> 29:55.348
and our paths won't cross again.

29:57.104 --> 29:58.128
Take care.

30:03.828 --> 30:04.912
(Great opportunity.)

30:17.904 --> 30:19.024
(I'm out of here.)

30:45.708 --> 30:46.768
(Hurry...)

30:53.136 --> 30:54.160
(I have to hide.)

30:56.944 --> 30:57.968
(Wait...)

30:58.640 --> 30:59.728
(Strange.)

31:00.240 --> 31:01.296
(I regained)

31:02.108 --> 31:03.708
(so much stamina overnight?)

31:04.708 --> 31:06.387
(Is that courtyard filled with)

31:06.387 --> 31:07.408
(spiritual energy?)

31:08.267 --> 31:09.468
(Or it has something)

31:09.468 --> 31:11.824
(to do with the food
that sickly fella makes.)

31:11.824 --> 31:13.328
(Tasty pastries.)

31:13.328 --> 31:14.387
(Amazing risotto.)

31:20.988 --> 31:22.108
Weird chicken.

31:27.120 --> 31:28.144
My chicken.

31:32.208 --> 31:33.296
Move!

31:40.147 --> 31:41.267
I swear I'll catch you.

31:43.748 --> 31:44.816
Hold it tight.

31:51.760 --> 31:52.816
Catch it.

31:55.088 --> 31:56.108
Don't let it get away.

31:56.108 --> 31:57.200
Don't move.

32:02.988 --> 32:04.048
Don't let it run away.

32:06.027 --> 32:07.088
Catch it!

32:08.272 --> 32:09.296
Move!

32:11.344 --> 32:12.368
Caught it.

32:15.760 --> 32:16.784
Slowly.

32:16.784 --> 32:18.544
Careful, slowly.

32:18.544 --> 32:19.568
Careful.

32:19.568 --> 32:20.592
Slowly.

32:20.592 --> 32:21.616
Got it!

32:25.348 --> 32:26.448
I got you!

32:27.147 --> 32:28.427
Chicken soup tonight.

32:29.187 --> 32:30.224
Soup for dinner, okay?

32:30.748 --> 32:31.828
Let me make soup for my husband.

32:32.400 --> 32:33.427
That won't do.

32:33.427 --> 32:34.576
Get lost!

32:34.576 --> 32:35.828
I am a phoenix!

32:36.348 --> 32:37.488
Stop trying to stew me.

32:37.488 --> 32:38.547
How can you talk about

32:39.067 --> 32:40.267
killing me so casually?

32:40.267 --> 32:41.307
Cluck cluck, shut up.

32:46.960 --> 32:48.016
It flew away.

32:48.907 --> 32:49.988
My chicken!

32:49.988 --> 32:51.387
Get it back.

32:52.560 --> 32:53.616
There is it.

33:11.312 --> 33:14.352
♪Raindrops dot the mountains and fields♪

33:15.088 --> 33:16.848
♪Entwined in the falling♪

33:17.488 --> 33:19.984
♪Disturbing my feelings♪

33:21.744 --> 33:25.296
♪Umbrella brim
parts the drifting clouds♪

33:25.296 --> 33:29.200
♪We look into each other's eyes♪

33:29.200 --> 33:31.888
♪Breathing of affection♪

33:32.400 --> 33:35.856
♪Raindrops transform into a line♪

33:35.856 --> 33:38.096
♪Forming worldly ties♪

33:38.640 --> 33:41.328
♪Circling you and me♪

33:43.120 --> 33:46.416
♪Coincidence appears to be destiny♪

33:46.416 --> 33:50.288
♪Guiding me to meet with you♪

33:50.288 --> 33:51.907
♪One glance lasts forever♪

33:51.907 --> 33:52.912
Silly chicken.

33:53.424 --> 33:55.566
♪Scarlet feathers fluttering♪

33:56.144 --> 33:58.128
♪Causing ripples in my mind♪

33:58.128 --> 34:00.656
♪Indulging me in a sweet dream♪

34:00.656 --> 34:02.928
♪Accompanying each other♪

34:02.928 --> 34:04.016
♪At this moment♪

34:04.016 --> 34:08.112
♪Our silent gaze speaks more than words♪

34:08.112 --> 34:09.264
♪In this lifetime♪

34:09.264 --> 34:12.880
♪I only feel complete around you♪

34:13.456 --> 34:16.080
♪You are right there when I turn♪

34:16.080 --> 34:19.248
♪How I wish to immerse in your fondness♪

34:19.248 --> 34:24.624
♪This passion will never fade away♪

34:30.128 --> 34:31.248
(I'm tired.)

34:32.427 --> 34:34.508
(I don't know who this guy is.)

34:35.468 --> 34:36.788
(But right now,)

34:37.708 --> 34:39.827
(I may get stewed at worst.)

34:41.268 --> 34:43.788
(At least, this guy
makes tasty food for me.)

34:47.107 --> 34:48.176
Cluck Cluck.

34:48.176 --> 34:50.587
I didn't expect you to come back.

34:51.948 --> 34:53.068
You actually

34:53.068 --> 34:55.107
waited here for me to take you home.

34:57.308 --> 34:58.347
You're quite something.

34:59.347 --> 35:00.496
You got yourself into such a mess

35:00.496 --> 35:03.147
in such a short time.

35:03.147 --> 35:06.928
♪Holding hands with deep affection♪

35:06.928 --> 35:09.776
♪Fearless of any danger♪

35:09.776 --> 35:11.952
♪The world falls silent in romance♪

35:12.528 --> 35:14.544
♪My longing for you doesn't end♪

35:14.544 --> 35:17.147
♪We part and yearn for the reunion♪

35:17.147 --> 35:18.988
Let's go home.

35:54.801 --> 35:57.681
♪Snow scatters
across the heavens and earth♪

35:58.673 --> 36:01.873
♪The dazzling light
envelopes the city with hope♪

36:02.321 --> 36:04.209
♪The fierce silver spear♪

36:04.209 --> 36:06.079
♪Pacifies all the wars♪

36:06.079 --> 36:09.073
♪Right and wrong, like an illusion♪

36:09.937 --> 36:12.817
♪Love brings confusion and delusion♪

36:13.553 --> 36:16.689
♪All the romance
and entanglement end in solitude♪

36:16.881 --> 36:18.641
♪Life is like a splendid dream♪

36:18.769 --> 36:23.281
♪Where I drink with you
until we get drunk♪

36:24.013 --> 36:27.249
♪Toast to the love and hate
engraved into our bones♪

36:27.729 --> 36:31.089
♪Living up to our encounter♪

36:31.249 --> 36:34.065
♪Filling the empty spot in the heart♪

36:34.257 --> 36:37.329
♪And head toward our fate♪

36:38.929 --> 36:42.193
♪Toast to the fate that chains us
for the rest of our lives♪

36:42.865 --> 36:46.188
♪Break the boundary
that defines our love♪

36:46.188 --> 36:48.177
♪The stars are glittering♪

36:48.177 --> 36:49.937
♪The world is a witness♪

36:50.161 --> 36:54.033
♪As it was initially said♪

36:55.025 --> 36:57.646
♪Defend the sun and the moon♪

36:57.681 --> 37:01.201
♪Devote everything
to the long-lasting wishes♪

37:01.393 --> 37:03.729
♪Love is hardly complete♪

37:03.953 --> 37:08.401
♪We can only protect
all beings from perishing♪

37:08.753 --> 37:12.401
♪Toast to the love and hate
engraved into our bones♪

37:12.625 --> 37:16.240
♪Living up to our encounter♪

37:16.305 --> 37:19.196
♪Filling the empty spot in the heart♪

37:19.281 --> 37:22.545
♪And head toward our fate♪

